HEADWORD: power dive
<hw>power dive</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>An airplane maneuver in which the pilot deads downward at a steep
angle while the engines are operating at or near full power; -- a method
to descend rapidly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>power-dive</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>power dive</ent>⟦br⟧
